{"rule_id": "659c3878-eb55-499b-953c-aac44db9fc63", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "MX", "original_language": "es", "rule_domain": "prohibited_products", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "prohibition", "title": "禁止销售的商品大类（墨西哥站）", "summary": "美客多禁止发布多类违法或高风险商品，违规会被下架并可能停号。", "content": "## 禁售商品大类\n- 武器、弹药与爆炸物；烟花\n- 毒品及违禁物质；管制药品、医美/健康产品\n- 手机/电信设备及违法服务、信号干扰/解码设备\n- 动植物及其衍生物；人体骨骼、器官与遗骸\n- 烟草及相关产品\n- 金融产品与服务、保险、博彩/彩票\n- 个人数据库与邮件列表、黑客程序或服务\n- 成人用品/服务、暴力或歧视性内容\n- 无证车辆、需国家许可或型式认证的产品\n\n卖家须对所售商品的合法性负全责，并持有适用法规要求的登记、许可与授权。", "severity": "critical", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.mercadolibre.com.mx/ayuda/Art-culos-prohibidos_1029", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["禁售", "合规", "商品政策"]}
{"rule_id": "778974f2-8294-4b45-99af-907206692241", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "BR", "original_language": "pt", "rule_domain": "prohibited_products", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "prohibition", "title": "禁止销售的商品（巴西站）", "summary": "巴西站要求商品具备监管机构认证，无证或假货禁止销售，违规可致部分/临时/永久停售。", "content": "## 巴西站禁售要点\n- 未取得 Anvisa、Anatel、INMETRO、Mapa、ANS 等机构认证/授权的产品\n- 锂电池、电池；易燃、易爆、气雾剂、腐蚀性和/或有毒产品\n- 需医生处方的隐形眼镜或有度数眼镜\n- 假冒产品（非权利人制造或未经其授权）\n\n违反这些政策可能导致在站点销售权被部分、临时或永久暂停。", "severity": "critical", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.mercadolivre.com.br/ajuda/Produtos-proibidos_1029", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["禁售", "巴西", "认证", "假货"]}
{"rule_id": "85b53a8b-6e46-4a07-b0cf-12cad70fa406", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "BR", "original_language": "pt", "rule_domain": "prohibited_products", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "prohibition", "title": "禁止发往 Full 仓库的商品（巴西站）", "summary": "部分商品因安全或属性原因不可入 Full 履约仓。", "content": "## 禁止入 Full 仓的商品（要点）\n- 锂电池及含锂电池产品、易燃/易爆/气雾剂/腐蚀性/有毒品\n- 无相应监管认证的产品\n- 假冒及侵权商品\n\n说明：官方 SPA 页直抓返回受限，具体清单以官方帮助页为准，建议核验。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.mercadolivre.com.br/ajuda/5200", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "medium", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["Full", "履约仓", "禁入仓"]}
{"rule_id": "0bd258e6-03b9-489e-b0fb-20561aefc476", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "MX", "original_language": "es", "rule_domain": "prohibited_products", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "prohibition", "title": "禁止发往 Full 仓库的商品（墨西哥站）", "summary": "进入 Full 履约前需确认商品不在禁入仓清单内。", "content": "## 禁止入 Full 仓（墨西哥站，要点）\n- 危险品（易燃、易爆、腐蚀、气雾剂等）\n- 不符合 Full 尺寸/重量与状态要求的商品\n\n说明：官方 SPA 页抓取返回 403，具体禁入清单以官方帮助页为准，confidence 标为待核验。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.mercadolibre.com.mx/ayuda/Que-productos-esta-prohibido-enviar-a-la-bodega_5200", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["Full", "履约仓", "墨西哥", "待核验"]}
{"rule_id": "714fc50b-e284-458f-9b17-d300e9e7ae99", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "MX", "original_language": "es", "rule_domain": "fees", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "fee", "title": "刊登类型与销售佣金（墨西哥站）", "summary": "美客多墨西哥分为免费、经典、旗舰三种刊登，佣金按类型与品类不同。", "content": "## 刊登类型与佣金（概述，待核验）\n- 免费(Gratuita)：无佣金，曝光低，刊登 60 天；新品/二手有年度免费销售上限\n- 经典(Clásica)：销售佣金约 8%–16%，低价商品另加固定金额费用\n- 旗舰(Premium)：销售佣金约 12.5%–20.5%，无低价附加固定费\n\n注：具体佣金率按品类浮动，请以官方费用模拟器为准。数值为二手概括，待核验。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.mercadolibre.com.mx/ayuda/como-publicar-en-mercado-libre_25316", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["佣金", "费用", "刊登类型", "待核验"]}
{"rule_id": "95c2bfc8-609e-4708-b3d5-262031f7b181", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "MX", "original_language": "es", "rule_domain": "fees", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "fee", "title": "Full 仓储费用", "summary": "使用 Full 除销售费用外，还按单品尺寸与重量计收每日仓储费。", "content": "## Full 费用构成\n- 继续支付正常的销售佣金\n- 额外按每件商品的尺寸与重量计算每日仓储费\n\n注：仓储费率随尺寸/重量与库龄变化，具体金额以官方计算器为准，待核验。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.mercadolibre.com.mx/ayuda/que-es-mercado-envios-full_5162", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["Full", "仓储费", "费用", "待核验"]}
{"rule_id": "22e7703b-6dcf-4e96-b87c-8bf4bf07eaa8", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "es", "rule_domain": "account_health", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "卖家声誉温度计（5 色等级）", "summary": "声誉以 5 色温度计展示，绿色最高、红色最低，直接影响曝光与功能。", "content": "## 声誉温度计\n- 颜色等级：红、橙、黄、浅绿、深绿（深绿最高，红色最低）\n- 红色为处罚区：曝光下降、功能受限、自然排名下滑\n- 深绿对应最高等级（部分国家含「Líder」标识）\n- 需至少完成 10 笔销售，系统才开始构建声誉档案", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.mercadolibre.com.mx/ayuda/16914", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "medium", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["声誉", "温度计", "账号健康"]}
{"rule_id": "84bfae07-3e46-4f9f-9e20-c5c41aeca858", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "es", "rule_domain": "account_health", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "声誉计算的三大指标", "summary": "声誉由投诉、卖家取消和延迟发货三类指标综合计算。", "content": "## 声誉三指标\n1. 买家投诉(reclamos)\n2. 卖家主动取消的订单\n3. 发货延迟(despachos con demoras)\n\n阈值参考（二手概括，待核验）：综合不良指标控制在 2% 以下可关联约 70% 的市场潜力；延迟交付不应超过 20%。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://developers.mercadolibre.com.mx/es_ar/manejo-de-ordenes/reputacion-de-vendedores", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["声誉", "指标", "投诉", "取消", "待核验"]}
{"rule_id": "c7c8c3b7-fba9-4561-9785-6409653e2bdf", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "MX", "original_language": "es", "rule_domain": "account_health", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "客服与售后指标管理", "summary": "卖家应在售后区监控关注指标，及时处理以减少销售问题。", "content": "## 关注指标\n- 在「售后(Posventa)」区可查看投诉与服务指标\n- 及时回应买家问题、快速处理可降低指标恶化风险\n- 指标恶化会拉低声誉与曝光\n\n建议定期检查并优化各项服务指标。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://vendedores.mercadolibre.com.mx/nota/analiza-tus-metricas-de-atencion-y-reduce-problemas-en-tus-ventas", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "medium", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["指标", "客服", "售后", "账号健康"]}
{"rule_id": "06616146-71c1-45db-8a4d-e3fac76d0c14", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "es", "rule_domain": "penalties", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "penalty", "title": "刊登违规的「moderación」处罚机制", "summary": "刊登违反政策会触发 moderación，处罚从降曝光到下架直至停号。", "content": "## moderación 处罚梯度\n- 刊登曝光下降\n- 刊登被暂停或直接下架\n- 账号临时停用\n- 账号永久停用（重大或重复违规）\n\n常见违规：发布二手品却用通用图、销售禁售品、引导站外交易等。", "severity": "critical", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://developers.mercadolibre.com.ar/es_ar/gestionar-moderaciones", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "medium", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["处罚", "moderación", "下架", "停号"]}
{"rule_id": "8175bf14-d7d9-48e2-9aa6-3c95a12356c5", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "es", "rule_domain": "penalties", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "penalty", "title": "账号临时与永久停用规则", "summary": "临时停用一般 2–5 天，重大或重复违规将永久停号。", "content": "## 停用类型\n- 临时停用：期间刊登暂停、无法回答买家提问、无法编辑刊登、无法使用 Mercado Shops 与 Mercado Envíos；进行中的销售不受影响\n- 永久停用：重大或重复违规时适用，无法再访问账号与在平台运营\n\n注：临时停用天数官方未在该页明确，相关二手资料概括为 2–5 天，待核验。", "severity": "critical", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.mercadolibre.com.mx/seguro_publicacion.html", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["停号", "临时停用", "永久停用", "待核验"]}
{"rule_id": "ab1f1dfb-1dda-42ec-bec8-42e73d1c4528", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "MX", "original_language": "es", "rule_domain": "penalties", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "prohibition", "title": "禁止引导站外交易与泄露联系方式", "summary": "在刊登或沟通中插入联系方式、引导站外交易将被调查并可能停号。", "content": "## 站外交易禁令\n- 禁止插入任何联系方式：邮箱、地址、邮编、电话/传真、银行信息、网址/网站\n- 禁止把买家引导至平台外完成交易（如发 WhatsApp、外链）\n- 违规将被调查，可能暂停或取消该笔操作乃至账号注册\n- 卖家不得未经同意向第三方透露买家个人数据，数据仅可用于平台交易相关用途", "severity": "critical", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.mercadolibre.com.mx/seguro_publicacion.html", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["站外交易", "联系方式", "处罚", "数据保护"]}
{"rule_id": "bdfd3b99-343c-41ec-b40b-6327755fcc4d", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "MX", "original_language": "es", "rule_domain": "intellectual_property", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "品牌保护计划（BPP）与侵权投诉流程", "summary": "权利人可通过免费的 BPP 投诉侵权刊登，被投诉刊登会暂停，卖家须限期举证。", "content": "## 品牌保护计划(BPP)\n- 完全免费，保护商标、著作权、工业品外观/设计、专利与实用新型\n- 权利人须注册后用授权账号发起投诉，可单条或批量、跨国家投诉\n\n## 投诉流程\n1. 刊登收到投诉后被暂停\n2. 卖家须在 4 个自然日内提交支持性文件举证\n3. 未回应或材料不足，刊登将被下架", "severity": "critical", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.mercadolibre.com.mx/ayuda/Programa-de-Proteccion-de-Propiedad-Intelectual_994", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["知识产权", "品牌保护", "侵权投诉", "BPP"]}
{"rule_id": "1eaa046b-325c-4893-b40c-b849b1b2ace2", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "MX", "original_language": "es", "rule_domain": "intellectual_property", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "如何发布而不侵犯知识产权", "summary": "卖家应使用自有内容、确保商品正品授权，避免侵权投诉。", "content": "## 避免侵权要点\n- 仅销售正品或经权利人授权的商品，禁止假冒\n- 不盗用他人图片、文案等受版权保护内容\n- 标题/描述/图片不得未经授权使用他人商标\n- 被投诉时及时提供进货发票、授权书等支持文件", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://vendedores.mercadolibre.com.mx/nota/como-publicar-sin-infringir-propiedad-intelectual", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "medium", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["知识产权", "正品", "商标", "版权"]}
{"rule_id": "a3e734f3-3f3b-4853-bb6c-7b2d51046f9e", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "BR", "original_language": "pt", "rule_domain": "intellectual_property", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "prohibition", "title": "禁止侵犯知识产权的内容（巴西站）", "summary": "巴西站禁止发布侵犯第三方知识产权的内容，含假货与盗用内容。", "content": "## 巴西站知识产权禁令\n- 禁止销售假冒产品（非权利人制造或未经授权）\n- 禁止使用侵犯第三方商标、著作权的内容\n- 收到投诉后须举证，否则刊登被移除", "severity": "critical", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.mercadolivre.com.br/ajuda/1078", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "medium", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["知识产权", "巴西", "假货", "侵权"]}
{"rule_id": "b0d1c320-31e1-4407-a1b9-a750a22b5299", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "MX", "original_language": "es", "rule_domain": "returns_refunds", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "退货政策与时限", "summary": "买家未收货 28 天内有保障；后悔或商品不符 30 天内可退货。", "content": "## 退货时限（待核验）\n- 未收到商品：自购买起 28 天保障期\n- 后悔/收到不符、不全、有缺陷商品：自收货起 30 天内可申请退货\n\n## 卖家义务\n- 须接受取消与退货\n- 须承担退货运费及（适用时）原始运费\n- 平台对退回商品做质检，不符退货政策的可退回买家", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.mercadolibre.com.mx/ayuda/politicas-devolucion_16914", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["退货", "退款", "时限", "待核验"]}
{"rule_id": "a5c543c8-76bd-4ac6-a1d1-453beee8afa2", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "MX", "original_language": "es", "rule_domain": "returns_refunds", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "「Compra Protegida」买家保护计划", "summary": "平台在买家收货确认前托管货款，未达预期或后悔可退款。", "content": "## Compra Protegida\n- 在买家收到商品前，平台托管买家货款\n- 若买家未收货、收到不符商品或后悔，可获退款\n- 退款方式取决于付款方式，通常退回原付款方式；也可退至 Mercado Pago 以即时到账\n\n部分商品被排除在该计划之外。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.mercadolibre.com.mx/ayuda/productos-que-no-tienen-devolucion_4292", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "medium", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["买家保护", "退款", "Compra Protegida"]}
{"rule_id": "2e33a4aa-604f-42d5-a855-55619c5361af", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "MX", "original_language": "es", "rule_domain": "returns_refunds", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "卖家侧退货如何运作", "summary": "买家退货时生成退货标签，平台质检后处理退款。", "content": "## 退货运作\n- 买家通过邮寄以同等状态退回商品\n- 系统生成退货标签\n- 平台对退回商品做质量控制\n- 质检通过后处理退款；不符要求的可退回买家\n\n卖家可在售后区跟踪退货状态。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.mercadolibre.com.mx/ayuda/C-mo-funcionan-las-devolucione_3285", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "medium", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["退货", "退货标签", "质检"]}
{"rule_id": "584c8ccd-5886-46df-b5c6-584d8812f92e", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "MX", "original_language": "es", "rule_domain": "after_sales", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "投诉与调解（mediación）处理", "summary": "卖家可在售后区处理投诉、升级调解，并在结案后申请排除影响。", "content": "## 投诉与调解\n- 在「售后→投诉与调解」可识别紧急、待办与已解决的投诉\n- 可将投诉升级为调解(mediación)请平台介入\n- 结案后可在售后区申请「排除(exclusión)」以减轻对声誉的影响\n- 解决投诉的 3 种方式：换货、全额/部分退款、生成退货标签", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://vendedores.mercadolibre.com.mx/nota/herramientas-para-resolver-los-reclamos-y-cuidar-mas-tu-reputacion", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["售后", "投诉", "调解", "声誉"]}
{"rule_id": "5aafaa6e-9883-4202-8e7e-a5099383c415", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "MX", "original_language": "es", "rule_domain": "after_sales", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "取消类投诉的处理时限", "summary": "买家要求取消的投诉，卖家 2 个工作日内退款可保声誉不受影响。", "content": "## 取消类投诉\n- 买家发起要求取消的投诉，初始不影响声誉\n- 卖家有 2 个工作日退款给买家\n- 及时退款则平台认可良好处理，声誉保持完整\n\n注：时限为二手概括，待核验。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://vendedores.mercadolibre.com.mx/nota/como-cuidar-tu-reputacion-en-los-reclamos-con-cancelacion", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["售后", "取消", "退款时限", "待核验"]}
{"rule_id": "8dabe187-f37e-4d91-ae75-31a4fcad0f97", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "MX", "original_language": "es", "rule_domain": "after_sales", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "预防买家发起投诉的建议", "summary": "通过准确描述、及时沟通与按时发货减少投诉。", "content": "## 降低投诉建议\n- 商品描述、图片与实物一致，信息完整准确\n- 及时回答买家提问\n- 按承诺时效发货，避免延迟\n- 主动沟通物流与异常情况\n\n减少投诉有助于维持声誉。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://vendedores.mercadolibre.com.mx/nota/consejos-para-evitar-que-tus-compradores-inicien-un-reclamo", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "medium", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["售后", "投诉预防", "沟通"]}
{"rule_id": "61f4c447-4e02-4bf3-a011-c5ee9c471f06", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "MX", "original_language": "es", "rule_domain": "logistics_fulfillment", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "Mercado Envíos Full 履约运作", "summary": "Full 由平台仓储、打包、发货并处理售后，提升时效与曝光。", "content": "## Full 履约运作\n- 商品入平台配送中心，售出后由平台拣货、打包、打印面单并发货\n- 主要地区 1 个工作日、其他地区 2 个工作日送达（首日 24 小时内可达）\n- 带 Full 标识，搜索排名通常更好\n- 售后由平台团队对接买家处理投诉/退货", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.mercadolibre.com.mx/ayuda/que-es-mercado-envios-full_5162", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "medium", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["Full", "履约", "物流", "时效"]}
{"rule_id": "cb681a0b-749a-4963-b286-a707e74f835f", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "MX", "original_language": "es", "rule_domain": "logistics_fulfillment", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "Full 入仓商品要求", "summary": "入 Full 商品须为全新工业化品，限重 25kg 并符合尺寸；有效期须大于 90 天。", "content": "## Full 入仓要求（待核验）\n- 须为全新、工业化生产的商品\n- 单件最大重量 25kg，并符合允许尺寸\n- 有保质期商品，剩余有效期须大于 90 天\n- 需提交意向表单，账号符合要求后由平台协助开通\n\n注：数值阈值为二手概括，以官方为准。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://vendedores.mercadolibre.com.mx/nota/envios-full-seguridad-y-velocidad-en-tus-entregas", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["Full", "入仓要求", "限重", "待核验"]}
{"rule_id": "ef05c2a1-5af0-4fa8-9820-eed575b1df22", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "MX", "original_language": "es", "rule_domain": "listing", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "刊登信息一致性与质量分", "summary": "刊登的标题、描述、图片与产品特性须一致，信息不足或有误会被暂停为待审。", "content": "## 刊登质量要求\n- 产品特性须与标题、描述、图片一致\n- 信息过少或数据错误，刊登可能被暂停并置「待审(Para revisar)」状态\n- 「刊登」区可查看每条刊登的质量分，按建议目标优化以提升成交概率\n- 需填写真实可售库存，否则刊登排名靠后", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.mercadolibre.com.mx/ayuda/como-publicar-en-mercado-libre_25316", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["刊登", "质量分", "一致性", "库存"]}
{"rule_id": "0ff9f884-69b0-47b3-aa97-bcbea9711638", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "MX", "original_language": "es", "rule_domain": "listing", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "产品技术规格（ficha técnica）填写", "summary": "按品类填写动态技术规格，字段越完整越利于曝光与转化。", "content": "## 技术规格(Ficha técnica)\n- 在美客多以「产品特性(Características del producto)」呈现，分主要特性、次要特性等\n- 字段随所选品类动态变化，发布或编辑时填写\n- 建议提供通用产品码(UPC/EAN)，便于识别并加速发布\n- 信息须真实、与实物一致", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://vendedores.mercadolibre.com.mx/nota/ficha-tecnica-la-forma-de-mostrar-lo-que-vendes", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "medium", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["刊登", "技术规格", "ficha técnica", "产品码"]}
{"rule_id": "5c29f231-2cb0-42b8-b6c8-e762187c4402", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "MX", "original_language": "es", "rule_domain": "category_qualification", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "受限品类的资质与许可要求", "summary": "食品、电子等特殊品类需相应许可或授权方可销售。", "content": "## 受限品类资质\n- 食品、电子产品等特殊品类需相应许可/授权\n- 需型式认证或国家授权的产品须先取得资质\n- 卖家须持有适用法规要求的登记、许可与授权\n- 缺资质发布可能被下架并影响账号\n\n注：具体品类要求以官方页面为准。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://vendedores.mercadolibre.com.mx/nota/que-documentos-necesitas-para-operar-como-empresa-en-mexico", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "medium", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["品类资质", "许可", "授权", "受限品类"]}
{"rule_id": "9adf51d8-d573-48eb-98c7-5dea1fea13e1", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "MX", "original_language": "es", "rule_domain": "category_qualification", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "目录刊登（catálogo）条款", "summary": "加入目录刊登须遵守目录专属条款与商品匹配规则。", "content": "## 目录刊登条款\n- 商品须与目录页中的产品准确匹配（同一型号/规格）\n- 须遵守目录刊登专属条款与条件\n- 错配或违规可能被移出目录或处罚\n\n注：详细条款以官方目录条款页为准。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.mercadolibre.com.mx/ayuda/catalogo_4676", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "medium", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["目录", "catálogo", "品类资质", "匹配"]}
{"rule_id": "cf976cb1-7c1f-4b53-b6c8-44b69358f5b5", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "MX", "original_language": "es", "rule_domain": "advertising", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "Product Ads 广告（按点击付费）", "summary": "Product Ads 为站内 PPC 广告，仅在用户点击时计费，可设预算与定向。", "content": "## Product Ads\n- 站内付费推广，把刊登变为赞助广告提升曝光\n- 按点击付费(PPC)，仅用户点击时计费，不会超过设定预算\n- 可按品类、地区、购买意向与关键词定向\n- 在广告管理器设置投入并监控表现，建议每周至少查看一次调整", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://vendedores.mercadolibre.com.mx/nota/como-funciona-el-administrador-de-campanas-de-product-ads", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "medium", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["广告", "Product Ads", "PPC", "推广"]}
{"rule_id": "68d1bec6-92d8-4f9e-a418-b69b6542d05b", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "MX", "original_language": "es", "rule_domain": "tax_compliance", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "ISR/IVA 税款代扣（墨西哥）", "summary": "平台依法代扣 ISR 与 IVA；未登记 RFC 者代扣比例显著更高。", "content": "## 税款代扣（2026，待核验）\n- 已登记 RFC：ISR 按售价约 1.0%、IVA 代扣 8%（总 IVA 的一半）\n- 未登记 RFC：合计代扣约 36%（ISR 20% + IVA 16%）\n- 代扣金额在 Mercado Pago 活动中体现，平台上缴 SAT/SATEG\n- 退货会从当月收入扣减并相应调整代扣\n\n注：税率随税改变化，数值为二手概括，待核验。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://vendedores.mercadolibre.com.mx/nota/que-son-y-como-se-aplican-las-retenciones", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["税务", "ISR", "IVA", "代扣", "待核验"]}
{"rule_id": "a44c4bbd-a313-4e65-aff1-17c2c013ed1e", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "MX", "original_language": "es", "rule_domain": "tax_compliance", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "开票义务与代扣凭证", "summary": "买家索票卖家须开具发票；每月初可下载代扣凭证用于报税。", "content": "## 开票与凭证\n- 买家要求开票时，卖家有义务开具（须有有效 CSD 数字签章证书）\n- 每月初可在「开票→税务」下载代扣凭证，用于向 SAT 证明已代扣税款\n- 即使已被代扣，仍须按时（每月 17 日前）申报", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://vendedores.mercadolibre.com.mx/nota/conoce-informacion-relevante-acerca-de-tus-facturas-fiscales", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "medium", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["税务", "开票", "CSD", "申报"]}
{"rule_id": "5aafaa6e-0001-4202-8e7e-a5099383ffff", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "MX", "original_language": "es", "rule_domain": "payments", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "Mercado Pago 货款放款时限", "summary": "货款在确认销售成功后放款，时限随发货方式不同。", "content": "## 放款时限（待核验）\n- 平台确认销售成功后放款，典型 14–21 天\n- 按发货方式：Full 约 8–14 天；Mercado Envíos 约 14–21 天；自行发货约 21–30 天\n- 投诉判定对卖家有利后，24–72 小时内放款\n\n注：时限为二手概括，以官方账户报告为准。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.mercadopago.com.mx/ayuda/cuando-podre-usar-dinero_275", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["放款", "Mercado Pago", "结算", "待核验"]}
{"rule_id": "5c29f231-0002-4b6c-b6c8-e762187fffff", "platform": "mercadolibre", "site": "MX", "original_language": "es", "rule_domain": "payments", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "Mercado Pago 资金冻结（dinero retenido）", "summary": "投诉、退款请求或拒付会导致相应货款被临时冻结至处理完毕。", "content": "## 资金冻结情形\n- 买家发起投诉或退款请求：相关货款冻结至处理完毕\n- 拒付(contracargo)：买行卡撤销交易期间冻结调查\n- 配送争议（未送达/状态异常）：冻结至确认结果\n- 可在「我的资金/余额」查看「冻结资金」明细（类型、日期、金额、原因）", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.mercadopago.com.mx/ayuda/que-es-el-dinero-retenido_19204", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "medium", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["资金冻结", "Mercado Pago", "拒付", "投诉"]}
